ack.title: Authors’ contributions
ack.p: Conceived and designed the experiments: QXH, ZXP, DY and ZXJ. Performed the experiments: YC, LN, LM and ZXJ. Analyzed the data: QXH, YC, LN, ZXJ and ZXP. Contributed reagents/materials/analysis tools: LM, ZXJ and DY. Wrote the paper: QXH, YC, ZXJ and ZXP. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.
